Insider Activity


Individual




Maria Teresa Hilado



Ms. Maria T. Hilado is Chief Financial Officer at Allergan Plc, Independent Director at H.B. Fuller Co., and Co-Chairman-Strong Kids Campaign at YMCA of Greater New York. She is on the Board of Directors at KYTHERA Biopharmaceuticals, Inc., Allergan, Inc., and H.B. Fuller Co.
Ms. Hilado was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Finance & Treasury by PepsiCo, Inc., Treasurer & Vice President by Schering-Plough Corp., an Assistant Treasurer by General Motors Corp., Chief Financial Officer by GMAC Commercial Finance LLC, and Chief Financial Officer by General Motors Acceptance Corp. She also served on the board at Bausch & Lomb, Inc.
She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Ateneo de Manila and an MBA from the University of Virginia Darden School of Business.



