Maria Teresa Hilado



Ms. Maria T. Hilado is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at Allergan Plc, Independent Director at H.B. Fuller Co., and Co-Chairman-Strong Kids Campaign at YMCA of Greater New York. She is on the Board of Directors at KYTHERA Biopharmaceuticals, Inc., Allergan, Inc., and H.B. Fuller Co.
